seller.oneLinerTitle: Brand Marketing Expert with 7000 Happy Clients
seller.description:
Hello! My name is Tommy. I am a multi-displinary brand marketer with experience in branding and in the digital marketing landscape. 


I am passionate about crafting impactful experiences and digital marketing strategies at the intersection of brand and product. 

I have worked in London, Hong Kong and in Shanghai for companies such as the Adidas, L'Oreal, Pfizer and Danone

I currently offer brand strategy, logo designs, social media and company naming.

His recommendations didn’t fit our business and I would have liked a bit more effort on his part to understand my business so he could deliver better recommendations. But he delivered his research and even did more research to provide five more influencer names.
Wow! I was not expecting all this amazing information, phenomenal job! I can’t wait to post and see how my followers are going to increase. Very knowledgeable information!

probably the best interaction I have ever had from Fiverr
Tommy kept in touch, created a very in depth plan, shared useful information in an easy to understand way.
now it's time for me to put it to the test and see if I can grow my Instagram.
I would highly recommend if not for the hashtags, just to find where to start on Instagram

Tommy was very responsive and kind to me. He provided 10/10 support and answered all the questions I've had and even offer to help me find more hashtags for my niche. Even though it's a tough niche he's managed to excel it. His strategy, hashtags are all great, and I'm already seeing results within the first week.

To work with Tommy and get his very detailed report was amazing, my brand is in a field I thought would be difficult for him,but it was not, he gave a lot of valuable insights. He is very kind and answered my few extra  questions very quickly - I recommend this gig to everyone serious about instagram growth
